<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_40_r2l2"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>frawnberg<ex>er</ex></expan> als Jr vns aber <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von <expan>Abraha<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_40_r2l3">des Juden <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd laſſen eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_40_r2l4"><expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . daʒ wır Abraham Juden bey vns <expan>geſeſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . für vns beſant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_40_r2l5">vnd <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> mıt Jm dauon gerett <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / der hat vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_40_r2l7">als vor . daʒ er 
<add><ab facs="#facs_40_line_1576664138668_1594">da </ab></add> von 
<del rend="strikethrough">den <expan>dıng<ex>en</ex></expan></del> niht wıſſe . vnd auch mıt eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_40_r2l8">niht <expan>wıſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒe ſchıken <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / VVıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> deẅht eẅch daʒ Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_40_r2l9">ʒu Jm ıht ʒe <expan>ſprech<ex>en</ex></expan> hett / <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır eẅch <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_40_r2l10"><expan>ſcheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mıt <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>voll<ex>e</ex>m</expan> gewalt . von <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>Abraha<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Jude<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_40_r2l11"><expan>freẅntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des Reıchs <expan>Rıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> bey vns ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_40_r2l12"><expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> . wenn wır des ermant <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> ſo <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> Jud anheim ıſt </ab>
